2","tid":1942403,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ccfabc78d3751ca4d506a5bfc0b7de38717e5e","tid":1942403,"uid":135867,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"弱智5洗駁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"用返藍尸邏輯：我唔知,無聽過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我幫襯黃店，唔係想黃圈賺左錢捐哂出黎<br />\n我係<strong>想藍店執笠</strong>!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"387fff1f35097b61ce942d565ee21ca5e358f198","tid":1942403,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:46:23.000Z","msg":"一開始我地對黃店要求只係支持罷工、去遊行、貼文宣<br />\n慢慢冇捐過錢就話偽黃<br />\n然後呢？捐得少都係博宣傳，偽黃"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d38b9bedb5d365c53d1a1a54960394a778306c58","tid":1942403,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"龍門冰室是知名黃店，但張俊傑一聽到「黃色經濟圈」就皺眉；皆因他見過黃店賺大錢後沒有捐出來、也有警察家庭投資的偽黃店不斷被「懲罰」。他寧願談「良心社會」：「有好多『良心老闆』、『良心導師』可以俾機會年輕人，好多『良心髮型屋』、『良心電工』俾黃絲居民光顧，然後佢哋又捐返某個百份比嘅營業額落嚟。如果我哋可以形成一個有足夠財力養活 200 萬人嘅社群，仲有咩走唔過去呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%94%B1%E6%B4%BE%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87%E5%88%B0%E6%89%BE%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E9%BE%8D%E9%96%80%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%87-%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%88-%E6%88%91%E8%AA%AA%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2589%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E